00:30:34.050 --> 00:30:39.100
Okay. And here's a bride
from Sutka, Macedonia.

00:30:39.100 --> 00:30:45.520
And now we'll see a scene
from the bride's day.

00:30:45.520 --> 00:30:49.930
Weddings in 1990 were
about five days long.

00:30:49.930 --> 00:30:51.980
Now they're only two days long.

00:30:51.980 --> 00:30:53.920
But this is the Saturday
of the wedding.

00:30:53.920 --> 00:30:56.670
The bride is in the middle.

00:30:56.670 --> 00:31:00.380
And her type of solo dancing,
cocek, is very modest.

00:31:00.380 --> 00:31:04.180
It is related to belly
dancing, but no skin is used.

00:31:04.180 --> 00:31:06.510
