00:31:06.510 --> 00:31:12.140
[ Music ]

00:31:12.140 --> 00:31:16.260
So here you can see actually
a little solo performance

00:31:16.260 --> 00:31:20.270
of cocek at a banquet.

00:31:20.270 --> 00:31:23.340
Again, this type of movement
is considered beautiful.

00:31:23.340 --> 00:31:28.220
Girls practice it, women
treasure it, men are encouraging.

00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:31.190
But the very same movement
before strange men

00:31:31.190 --> 00:31:35.510
in a bar would be considered
very, like a prostitute.

00:31:35.510 --> 00:31:37.440
It would be very unacceptable.

00:31:37.440 --> 00:31:38.740
Absolutely not.

00:31:38.740 --> 00:31:41.170
So it's not the movement
itself, but the context.

