00:35:25.410 --> 00:35:29.650
But I can certainly say that the
people running the festivals don't

00:35:29.650 --> 00:35:32.850
care about Romani communities,
and that's my critique

00:35:32.850 --> 00:35:36.910 position:56%
because I'm non-Roma and I feel like
I need to work with my own people

00:35:36.910 --> 00:35:39.910
and present a critique of it, okay?

00:35:39.910 --> 00:35:44.230
So in the Bronx, they have
