00:48:53.680 --> 00:48:55.770
and the refrain is "Tsiganizatia."

00:48:55.770 --> 00:48:58.370
But you have to understand
that Tsiganizatia,

00:48:58.370 --> 00:49:03.380
which means Gypsyfication, is used
by right-wing xenophobic parties

00:49:03.380 --> 00:49:07.220
to say our country is
becoming too Gypsyfied.

00:49:07.220 --> 00:49:09.320
Let's get rid of those folks.

00:49:09.320 --> 00:49:13.850
So, again, even hearing that
word is very, very problematic.

00:49:13.850 --> 00:49:16.840
But he's using it as
the refrain of his song.

